goscape-client — third-party notices and attribution
=====================================================

goscape-client is a Go port of the RuneScape 2 client. It was produced by
translating and cross-referencing the clients maintained by the Lost City
project (https://github.com/LostCityRS):

- Client-Java (https://github.com/LostCityRS/Client-Java) — the deobfuscated
  Java RuneScape 2 client, used as the authoritative reference for the
  translation. The original RuneScape 2 client is the intellectual property of
  Jagex Ltd. This project is an unofficial, fan-made preservation/study effort,
  is not affiliated with or endorsed by Jagex, and distributes no Jagex game
  assets or content.

- Client-TS (https://github.com/LostCityRS/Client-TS) — the MIT-licensed
  TypeScript client, used as a secondary cross-check for ambiguous Java -> Go
  translations. Its license is reproduced below as required by its terms.

